## Release Policy & Versioning

Releases are milestone-gated to ensure production stability:
1. **Milestone-Gated:** Version tags are only cut when all issues belonging to a milestone are closed.
2. **Conventional SemVer:** Bumps are computed programmatically from the Git squash-merge commit log.
3. **Automated Documentation:** The project wiki is updated automatically on release using the sync scripts.
